OL,3,CTougher rules proposed for benefit
OL,4,Ccheats in Guernsey
OL,6,FBenefit fraudsters in Guernsey could
OL,7,Fface tougher penalties if new
OL,8,Fproposals are approved.
OL,10,FIt comes after the Employment and
OL,11,FSocial Security Committee is proposing
OL,12,Fto increase the maximum penalty of
OL,13,Fbenefit-related fraud offences to
OL,14,Fseven years in prison, bringing the
OL,15,Fisland in line with Jersey and the UK.
OL,17,FThe Committee says the changes would
OL,18,Fprovide the courts with greater
OL,19,Fflexibility to deal with the offences
OL,20,Fappropriately and help deter people
OL,21,Ffrom making false claims.
