OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F389A1760034812
OL,3,CTougher rules proposed for benefit
OL,4,Ccheats in Guernsey
OL,6,F"By aligning Guernsey's sentencing
OL,7,Fpowers with those of the UK and Jersey
OL,8,Fwe are sending a clear message that
OL,9,Fbenefit fraud is no less serious than
OL,10,Fany other type of fraud.
OL,12,F"If the Committee's proposals are
OL,13,Fapproved by the States, the courts
OL,14,Fwill continue to impose a sentence
OL,15,Fthat fits the crime, but they will
OL,16,Fhave the freedom to appropriately
OL,17,Fpunish the most serious offenders."
